    p(style="font-size: 16px") Runoff time! Excellence voting again. Ties this round get decided by a committee headed by Matt Reilly, Rachel Gebhart and Carl Bailey.
    p(style="font-style: italic") 
      | You are logged in as 
      b
        = user.id
      | . 
      a(href="/logout/")
        | Logout?

  if saved
    div.alert.alert-success(style="text-align: center") Your vote has been saved! You can recast it as often as you'd like before 11:59 PM Monday, May 6.
  else
    p(style="text-align: center") Cast your vote below. You can recast it as often as you'd like before 11:59 PM Monday, May 6.

