              each url in submission.urls
                div.position(style="margin-bottom: 20px;border-color:black;border-width:10px;width:100%")
                  img(src="https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/11830885/2014%20T-shirt%20Contest/" + url.addr,height="500px",width="500px",style="border-width: 2px;border-color: black;border-style: line;")
                  br
                  input(name=url.voting,type="checkbox",checked=answers[url.voting])
                  span(style="margin-left:10px") I totally dig the design above this checkbox!
